Alembic environment for the PUBLIC schema.

Manages platform-wide tables (clients, orders, settings) declared on PublicBase.

Common commands (run from the repo root):

  # Create a new migration by diffing PublicBase models against the live DB
  alembic revision --autogenerate -m "describe the change"

  # Apply migrations
  alembic upgrade head

  # Roll back one revision
  alembic downgrade -1

  # Show current revision in the DB
  alembic current

  # Show history
  alembic history

The version tracking table lives at public.alembic_version.
